questions.quote: Oh, yeah. Yeah, I've uh...I've spent a little time in the Mideast. You ever been to the Mideast?
My mother loves Hampton tomatoes. She's nuts for Hampton tomatoes.
O.K. You take normal sips. Nothing wrong with that. Then what happened?
A woman that hates me this much comes along once in a lifetime.
I waited, he didn't show up. Anyway, this guy gave me an open-lip kiss.
So she just left the office - didn't say a word to you about anything?
Oh, because I called over there a couple of times and the manager didn't like it.
